Cancellation and Refund Policy

At Mihir Raghani, we strive to provide high-quality graphic design services to our clients. We understand that circumstances may arise where cancellations or refunds are necessary. Please review our policy regarding cancellations and refunds outlined below:

1. Cancellation Policy

Clients can request to cancel a project or service by providing written notice via email or written communication. The cancellation request will be subject to the following conditions:

Before Commencement of Work: If a cancellation request is made before any work has commenced, a full refund will be issued.
After Commencement of Work: If work has begun on the project, a cancellation fee may be applicable. The fee will be determined based on the progress made and the resources expended up to the point of cancellation.
2. Refund Policy

Refunds, if applicable, will be processed according to the following conditions:

Quality Concerns: If the delivered work does not meet the agreed-upon specifications or quality standards, clients may request revisions. If issues persist and cannot be resolved, a partial or full refund may be granted, at our discretion.
Unused Services: If a client has paid for services that have not been utilized or commenced, a refund may be provided for the unused portion, minus any applicable cancellation fees.
3. Refund Processing

Refunds, if approved, will be processed within [number of days] from the date of approval. The refund will be issued using the original payment method whenever possible.

4. No Refund Eligibility

Refunds will not be provided under the following circumstances:

If the client fails to provide necessary project details or materials required to complete the work.
If the client terminates the project due to reasons beyond our control (e.g., changes in business circumstances, personal preferences, or rebranding).
5. Modifications and Cancellation Fee

Mihir Raghani reserves the right to modify or cancel any project or service at our discretion. In such cases, clients will be informed promptly, and a full refund will be issued if payment has already been made.

6. Contact Information

For any inquiries or concerns regarding our cancellation and refund policy, please contact Mihir Raghani at +91 9427629611 or via email at mihirraghani@gmail.com.

